<h2 id="Syntax">Syntax</h2>
<pre class="twopartsyntaxbox"><a href="/en-US/docs/CSS/Value_definition_syntax" title="CSS/Value_definition_syntax">Formal syntax</a>: <code><a href="/en-US/docs/CSS/length" title="Possible value: a number followed by 'em', 'ex', 'ch', 'rem', 'px', 'cm', 'mm', 'in', 'vh', 'vw', 'vmin', 'vmax', 'pt', 'pc', 'px', like 3px, 1.5cm, -0.5em, 0.">&lt;length&gt;</a> <a href="/en-US/docs/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#Single_bar" title="Single bar: the two entities are optional, but exactly one must be present.">|</a> <a href="/en-US/docs/CSS/percentage" title="">&lt;percentage&gt;</a></code></pre>
<pre>shape-outside: circle()
shape-margin: 10px

shape-margin: <a href="/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/initial">initial</a>
shape-margin: <a href="/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/inherit">inherit</a>
shape-margin: <a href="/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/unset">unset</a>
</pre>
<h3 id="Values">Values</h3>
<dl><dt>
  <span style="font-family: 'Courier New', 'Andale Mono', monospace; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: 1.5;">&lt;length&gt;</span></dt>
 <dd>
  Sets the margin of the shape to the <a href="/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/length"><code>&lt;length&gt;</code></a>Â .</dd>
 <dt>
  <span style="font-family: 'Courier New', 'Andale Mono', monospace; line-height: normal;">&lt;percentage&gt;</span></dt>
 <dd>
  <span style="line-height: 1.5;">Sets the margin of the shape to a percentage of the width of the element's containing block.</span></dd>
</dl>